v class="Authors-module-scss-module__BkATYW__soloAuthor"><img alt="Negar Mojtahedi" loading="lazy" width="48" height="48" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="Authors-module-scss-module__BkATYW__avatar" style="color:transparent" src="https://i.iranintl.com/images/rdk9umy0/production/c8d97cf79269158b3befa7106414ac9945918ade-964x868.jpg?rect=48,0,868,868&amp;w=96&amp;h=96&amp;fit=max&amp;sat=-100&amp;auto=format"/><div class="Authors-module-scss-module__BkATYW__information"><a class="Authors-module-scss-module__BkATYW__link" href="https://www.iranintl.com/en/author/negar-mojtahedi">Negar Mojtahedi</a><p class="Authors-module-scss-module__BkATYW__position">Iran International</p></div></div></div></div></article></div><div class="DailyReportCluster-module-scss-module__mBywQG__additionalItem"><article class="cluster-item cluster-item--inline"><div class="cluster-item__main"><strong class="cluster-item__tags cluster-item__tags--inline" style="color:#82059f">PODCAST</strong><a class="cluster-item__link" href="https://www.iranintl.com/en/202601235132"><h4 class="cluster-item__headline cluster-item__headline--inline">&#x27;A moment like no other&#x27;: US-based think tank urges Trump to sap Iran</h4></a><div class="Authors-module-scss-module__BkATYW__authors "><div class="Authors-module-scss-module__BkATYW__soloAuthor"><img alt="Negar Mojtahedi" loading="lazy" width="48" height="48" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="Authors-module-scss-module__BkATYW__avatar" style="color:transparent" src="https://i.iranintl.com/images/rdk9umy0/production/c8d97cf79269158b3befa7106414ac9945918ade-964x868.jpg?rect=48,0,868,868&amp;w=96&amp;h=96&amp;fit=max&amp;sat=-100&amp;auto=format"/><div class="Authors-module-scss-module__BkATYW__information"><a class="Authors-module-scss-module__BkATYW__link" href="https://www.iranintl.com/en/author/negar-mojtahedi">Negar Mojtahedi</a><p class="Authors-module-scss-module__BkATYW__position">Iran International</p></div></div></div></div></article></div></section></div></section><section class="cluster undefined"><header class="ClusterHeader-module-scss-module__YSLH0a__header"><h3 class="ClusterHeader-module-scss-module__YSLH0a__header__title">Tehran Insider</h3></header><div class="InDepthCluster-module-scss-module__AU2hwW__container"><div class="InDepthCluster-module-scss-module__AU2hwW__featured"><article class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__card EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__card--featured EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__vertical undefined InDepthCluster-module-scss-module__AU2hwW__featuredItem"><figure class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__mediaContainer EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__aspect-3-2"><img alt="A letter from Iran: I don’t trust those who say they have the answers" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__image" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" src="https://i.iranintl.com/images/rdk9umy0/production/d517056f2b7c69bfacdf924a1f34c85db27cabe6-780x470.jpg?rect=0,38,639,426&amp;w=600&amp;h=400&amp;q=80&amp;fit=crop&amp;auto=format"/></figure><main class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__content"><header><strong class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__tag" style="color:#2300bc">TEHRAN INSIDER</strong><a class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__link" href="https://www.iranintl.com/en/202601137152"><h3 class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__headline">A letter from Iran: I don’t trust those who say they have the answers</h3></a></header><p class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__lead">I am writing this from Tehran after three days of trying to find a way to send it: things may get a lot worse before they get any better.</p></main></article></div><div class="InDepthCluster-module-scss-module__AU2hwW__cover"><div class="InDepthCluster-module-scss-module__AU2hwW__featuredItem"><article class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__card EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__card--featured EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__vertical undefined InDepthCluster-module-scss-module__AU2hwW__featuredItem2"><figure class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__mediaContainer EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__aspect-3-2"><img alt="Against Iran’s politics of exclusion, pluralism is the point" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__image" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" src="https://i.iranintl.com/images/rdk9umy0/production/f48fb47cb6d3710ae5ef8a20a764e98f9a2a8cb2-5184x3456.jpg?rect=323,381,4344,2896&amp;w=600&amp;h=400&amp;q=80&amp;fit=crop&amp;auto=format"/></figure><main class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__content"><header><strong class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__tag" style="color:#2300bc">TEHRAN INSIDER</strong><a class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__link" href="https://www.iranintl.com/en/202512241682"><h3 class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__headline">Against Iran’s politics of exclusion, pluralism is the point</h3></a></header><p class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__lead">There is a cruel ritual in Iranian opposition politics: some voices abroad constantly interrogate the “purity” of activists inside—why they did not speak more sharply or endorse maximalist slogans, why survival itself looks insufficiently heroic.</p></main></article></div></div><section class="InDepthCluster-module-scss-module__AU2hwW__additional"><div class="InDepthCluster-module-scss-module__AU2hwW__additionalItem"><article class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__card EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__card--featured EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__vertical undefined undefined"><figure class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__mediaContainer EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__aspect-3-2"><img alt="The Iran that never trends" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__image" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent" src="https://i.iranintl.com/images/rdk9umy0/production/d18b97b2b04b82203eb63462dfadd72f06aeab6f-1000x667.jpg?rect=84,62,867,578&amp;w=600&amp;h=400&amp;q=80&amp;fit=crop&amp;auto=format"/></figure><main class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__content"><header><strong class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__tag" style="color:#2300bc">TEHRAN INSIDER</strong><a class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__link" href="https://www.iranintl.com/en/202511213341"><h3 class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__headline">The Iran that never trends</h3></a></header></main></article></div><div class="InDepthCluster-module-scss-module__AU2hwW__additionalItem"><article class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__card EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__card--featured EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__vertical undefined undefined"><main class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__content"><header><strong class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__tag" style="color:#2300bc">TEHRAN INSIDER</strong><a class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__link" href="https://www.iranintl.com/en/202510246509"><h3 class="EditorialContentCard-module-scss-module__Hn1PmG__headline">Revolutionary road: a family row captures Iran&#x27;s political gridlock</h3></a></header></main></article></div></section></div></section></section><section class="home__topics"><div class="home__topics__container">