ition from some members who warn against “hereditary leadership,” Iran International has learned.\"}],\"markDefs\":[],\"style\":\"normal\"}],\"publishedAt\":\"2026-03-05T06:52:46.328Z\",\"shorthandUrl\":null,\"slug\":\"202603052337\",\"tag\":{\"color\":\"#cf2023\",\"id\":\"92efbced-9c0f-428b-9506-12d645faf6aa\",\"slug\":\"exclusive\",\"title\":\"EXCLUSIVE\"},\"tags\":[{\"color\":\"#cf2023\",\"id\":\"92efbced-9c0f-428b-9506-12d645faf6aa\",\"slug\":\"exclusive\",\"title\":\"EXCLUSIVE\"}],\"type\":\"article\"}],\"key\":\"f99cfe730d96\",\"style\":\"normal\",\"title\":\"Editors' Pick\",\"type\":\"customlist\"},{\"data\":{\"items\":[{\"authors\":null,\"headline\":\"Guards push fast Mojtaba Khamenei announcement amid dissent over hereditary rule \",\"id\":\"05f74df2-1cd8-4878-b169-c3ab8ec3fb33\",\"image\":{\"alt\":null,\"asset\":{\"_ref\":\"image-cab65bb8c2206f5a7733cd00ade47ba5c4ffb4b2-600x400-jpg\",\"_type\":\"reference\"},\"crop\":null,\"hotspot\":null,\"metadata\":{\"dimensions\":{\"height\":400,\"width\":600},\"lqip\":\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"}},\"language\":\"english\",\"lead\":[{\"_key\":\"9515e973f740\",\"_type\":\"block\",\"children\":[{\"_key\":\"8d56ae1c76d4\",\"_type\":\"span\",\"marks\":[],\"text\":\"Iran’s Assembly of Experts is set to hold an emergency session on Thursday to formally announce Mojtaba Khamenei, a son of the late Supreme Leader, as the next leader, despite opposition from some members who warn against “hereditary leadership,” Iran International has learned.\"}],\"markDefs\":[],\"style\":\"normal\"}],\"publishedAt\":\"2026-03-05T06:52:46.328Z\",\"shorthandUrl\":null,\"slug\":\"202603052337\",\"tag\":{\"color\":\"#cf2023\",\"id\":\"92efbced-9c0f-428b-9506-12d645faf6aa\",\"slug\":\"exclusive\",\"title\":\"EXCLUSIVE\"},\"tags\":[{\"color\":\"#cf2023\",\"id\":\"92efbced-9c0f-428b-9506-12d645faf6aa\",\"slug\":\"exclusive\",\"title\":\"EXCLUSIVE\"}],\"type\":\"article\"},{\"authors\":null,\"headline\":\"US State Department rejects Iran’s claim of 100 Americans killed in Dubai\",\"id\":\"90e3e516-9ac8-48eb-940b-59e0e58a1953\",\"image\":{\"alt\":null,\"asset\":{\"_ref\":\"image-c48aee4df60fdd5069b9f36ab518f6d146f71231-1920x1280-jpg\",\"_type\":\"reference\"},\"crop\":null,\"hotspot\":null,\"metadata\":{\"dimensions\":{\"height\":1280,\"width\":1920},\"lqip\":\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"}},\"language\":\"english\",\"lead\":[{\"_key\":\"49882adfa13f\",\"_type\":\"block\",\"children\":[{\"_key\":\"7cc29f511650\",\"_type\":\"span\",\"marks\":[],\"text\":\"The United States rejected Iranian claims that more than 100 Americans were killed in an attack in Dubai, calling the reports “complete disinformation,” a State Department spokesperson said on Wednesday.\"}],\"markDefs\":[],\"style\":\"normal\"}],\"publishedAt\":\"2026-03-05T09:57:55.325Z\",\"shorthandUrl\":null,\"slug\":\"202603051892\",\"tag\":null,\"tags\":null,\"type\":\"story\"},{\"authors\":[{\"id\":\"190ffc74-d9df-4f08-bef9-98e1aefcfe0e\",\"image\":{\"_type\":\"figure\",\"alt\":\"Maryam Sinaee, British Iranian journalist\",\"asset\":{\"_ref\":\"image-45ee979fa99e8002d6eaa062959bc17d6e4fd2ff-1520x2026-jpg\",\"_type\":\"reference\"},\"caption\":\"Maryam Sinaiee\"},\"name\":\"Maryam Sinaiee\",\"slug\":\"maryam-sinaiee\"}],\"headline\":\"Fears grow for Iranian prisoners as war raises risk of another Evin disaster\",\"id\":\"de4153fc-d202-4fe4-bb2e-2a9dc40fef3f\",\"image\":{\"alt\":null,\"asset\":{\"_ref\":\"image-3e7e160277f7265ee2ef5f6c4b5a192d9ded416f-780x470-jpg\",\"_type\":\"reference\"},\"crop\":{\"_type\":\"sanity.imageCrop\",\"bottom\":0,\"left\":0,\"right\":0,\"top\":0},\"hotspot\":{\"_type\":\"sanity.imageHotspot\",\"height\":0.9926697343562613,\"width\":1,\"x\":0.5,\"y\":0.5036651328218693},\"metadata\":{\"dimensions\":{\"height\":470,\"width\":780},\"lqip\":\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"}},\"language\":\"english\",\"lead\":[{\"_key\":\"50e1367fa93f\",\"_type\":\"block\",\"children\":[{\"_key\":\"940706e633e9\",\"_type\":\"span\",\"marks\":[],\"text\":\"Human rights groups and families of detainees warn that wartime conditions inside Iranian prisons could trigger another tragedy like the June strike on Tehran’s Evin prison.\"}],\"markDefs\":[],\"style\":\"normal\"}],\"publishedAt\":\"2026-03-05T19:47:00.000Z\",\"shorthandUrl\":null,\"slug\":\"202603051966\",\"tag\":null,\"tags\":null,\"type\":\"article\"},{\"authors\":[{\"id\":\"6414f9a3-dff0-493d-9b98-afe743be0eac\",\"image\":{\"_type\":\"figure\",\"asset\":{\"_ref\":\"image-361d9766a76ca6774c668ba1aa543ef5e7f60fa5-1022x1021-png\",\"_type\":\"reference\"}},\"name\":\"Hooman Abedi\",\"slug\":\"hooman-abedi\"}],\"headline\":\"Khamenei burial delay sparks wave of dark humor online\",\"id\":\"929ae957-fa93-43d1-aebe-26785fa70b3a\",\"image\":{\"alt\":\"Iranian media have released images showing preparations at Tehran’s prayers ground for the placement of the body of Iran’s former Supreme Leader, Ali Khamenei.\",\"asset\":{\"_ref\":\"image-216b087f059c2ee3961e629c84a75a019f957411-4659x3233-jpg\",\"_type\":\"reference\"},\"crop\":null,\"hotspot\":null,\"metadata\":{\"dimensions\":{\"height\":3233,\"width\":4659},\"lqip\":\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"}},\"language\":\"english\",\"lead\":[{\"_key\":\"12a410bf5f0d\",\"_type\":\"block\",\"children\":[{\"_key\":\"a4ddcee7d8e8\",\"_type\":\"span\",\"marks\":[],\"text\":\"Iranians have flooded social media with dark humor and mocking comments about the delayed burial of Supreme Leader Ali Khamenei after authorities on Wednesday canceled a planned procession and what they described as a public farewell to his body due to security concerns.\"}],\"markDefs\":[],\"style\":\"normal\"}],\"publishedAt\":\"2026-03-05T14:49:15.331Z\",\"shorthandUrl\":null,\"slug\":\"202603057832\",\"tag\":{\"color\":\"#0084bc\",\"id\":\"73b1863d-5f72-4a43-a578-40a59fc0e60b\",\"slug\":\"insight\",\"title\":\"INSIGHT\"},\"tags\":[{\"color\":\"#0084bc\",\"id\":\"73b1863d-5f72-4a43-a578-40a59fc0e60b\",\"slug\":\"insight\",\"title\":\"INSIGHT\"}],\"type\":\"article\"},{\"authors\":null,\"headline\":\"Iran could reach 8000 ballistic missiles by next year, Israeli military says\",\"id\":\"1b3dbb47-9d64-4a01-aadc-e2c00bb1849f\",\"image\":{\"alt\":null,\"asset\":{\"_ref\":\"image-4d1178454b8200d16675c05c1350ebfb49b34f66-800x533-jpg\",\"_type\":\"reference\"},\"crop\":{\"_type\":\"sanity.imageCrop\",\"bottom\":0,\"left\":0,\"right\":0.2836437914762647,\"top\":0.12947883715335318},\"hotspot\":{\"_type\":\"sanity.imageHotspot\",\"height\":0.8705211628466468,\"width\":0.7163562085237354,\"x\":0.3581781042618677,\"y\":0.5647394185766765},\"metadata\":{\"dimensions\":{\"height\":533,\"width\":800},\"lqip\":\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"}},\"language\":\"english\",\"lead\":[{\"_key\":\"6f942f20c793\",\"_type\":\"block\",\"children\":[{\"_key\":\"d5e4f02d8f4b\",\"_type\":\"span\",\"marks\":[],\"text\":\"An Israeli military spokesperson said on Thursday Iran could build up an arsenal of up to 8000 ballistic missiles by 2027 if it continued rebuilding its missile program following the June 2025 war.\"}],\"markDefs\":[],\"style\":\"normal\"}],\"publishedAt\":\"2026-03-05T18:22:06.407Z\",\"shorthandUrl\":null,\"slug\":\"202603059373\",\"tag\":null,\"tags\":null,\"type\":\"article\"},{\"authors\":[{\"id\":\"7d992022-8185-4f81-9c10-f6248343d310\",\"image\":{\"_type\":\"figure\",\"asset\":{\"_ref\":\"image-5c3bcbc430be392655ac260eb076f4aa1cac75eb-2578x3000-jpg\",\"_type\":\"reference\"},\"crop\":{\"_type\":\"sanity.imageCrop\",\"bottom\":0.041674285714285664,\"left\":0,\"right\":0.0028571428571428914,\"top\":0.11521714285714295},\"hotspot\":{\"_type\":\"sanity.imageHotspot\",\"height\":0.8431085714285714,\"width\":0.9971428571428571,\"x\":0.49857142857142855,\"y\":0.5367714285714287}},\"name\":\"Umud Shokri\",\"slug\":\"omid-shokri\"}],\"headline\":\"Everyone is watching oil in Iran war, but real risk is water\",\"id\":\"705e7039-8aa1-461f-b5a6-93ea891d2b95\",\"image\":{\"alt\":\"n employee stands next to a waste water collection pool at the world's largest water desalination plant at the Saline Water Conversion Corporation Ras Al-Khair Power and Desalination Plant in Ras al Khair, Saudi Arabia, October 8, 2020.\",\"asset\":{\"_ref\":\"image-a051aa798a0f75553eb85a7fa324696dc35e4fa9-1920x1280-jpg\",\"_type\":\"reference\"},\"crop\":null,\"hotspot\":null,\"metadata\":{\"dimensions\":{\"height\":1280,\"width\":1920},\"lqip\":\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"}},\"language\":\"english\",\"lead\":[{\"_key\":\"5124584ca177\",\"_type\":\"block\",\"children\":[{\"_key\":\"85bf4ecb08f6\",\"_type\":\"span\",\"marks\":[],\"text\":\"As war spreads across the Middle East and attention focuses on oil, the region’s most dangerous soft targets may be desalination plants.\"}],\"markDefs\":[],\"style\":\"normal\"}],\"publishedAt\":\"2026-03-05T03:48:15.168Z\",\"shorthandUrl\":null,\"slug\":\"202603044239\",\"tag\":{\"color\":\"#0084bc\",\"id\":\"7e8963b0-5dd5-43ed-9536-d5d4a4af8626\",\"slug\":\"analysis\",\"title\":\"ANALYSIS\"},\"tags\":[{\"color\":\"#0084bc\",\"id\":\"7e8963b0-5dd5-43ed-9536-d5d4a4af8626\",\"slug\":\"analysis\",\"title\":\"ANALYSIS\"}],\"type\":\"article\"},{\"authors\":null,\"headline\":\"Trump says Iran wants talks but it’s 'too late'\",\"id\":\"01f0137f-8a0b-4c5a-a5bd-e79352bc125a\",\"image\":{\"alt\":\"US President Donald Trump speaks in an event to honour reigning Major League Soccer (MLS) champion Inter Miami CF, March 5, 2026\",\"asset\":{\"_ref\":\"image-f48fd98a9a216c61dfec21ed237af2044b9be323-5529x3686-jpg\",\"_type\":\"reference\"},\"crop\":null,\"hotspot\":null,\"metadata\":{\"dimensions\":{\"height\":3686,\"width\":5529},\"lqip\":\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"}},\"language\":\"english\",\"lead\":[{\"_key\":\"72e3980fcd92\",\"_type\":\"block\",\"children\":[{\"_key\":\"a1544d9b06cc\",\"_type\":\"span\",\"marks\":[],\"text\":\"President Donald Trump said on Wednesday that Iran was seeking negotiations but warned it was “too late” as US-led strikes intensified in a widening conflict now entering its sixth day.\"}],\"markDefs\":[],\"style\":\"normal\"}],\"publishedAt\":\"2026-03-05T23:05:00.000Z\",\"shorthandUrl\":null,\"slug\":\"202603054889\",\"tag\":null,\"tags\":null,\"type\":\"article\"},{\"authors\":null,\"headline\":\"UK watchdog warns charities on Iran-linked activity, vows action on extremist ties\",\"id\":\"50fef915-2c85-456c-aefd-1a62c7a2dffb\",\"image\":{\"alt\":\"Police officers stand at a cordon on Whitehall in Westminster after the road was closed following an incident involving the arrest of a man near Downing Street, in London, Britain, April 18, 2022.  \",\"asset\":{\"_ref\":\"image-822675167545f2fb7ec8baddb9c9c1ed0b7ca062-5000x3335-jpg\",\"_type\":\"reference\"},\"crop\":null,\"hotspot\":null,\"metadata\":{\"dimensions\":{\"height\":3335,\"width\":5000},\"lqip\":\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"}},\"language\":\"english\",\"lead\":[{\"_key\":\"dcbdf0bb766e\",\"_type\":\"block\",\"children\":[{\"_key\":\"d933934d2a1a\",\"_type\":\"span\",\"marks\":[],\"text\":\"Britain’s charity regulator issued fresh guidance on Thursday warning charities to exercise caution in their activities related to Iran as tensions in the region intensify, and said it would act on any evidence of links to extremism or terrorism.\"}],\"markDefs\":[],\"style\":\"normal\"}],\"publishedAt\":\"2026-03-05T12:26:39.285Z\",\"shorthandUrl\":null,\"slug\":\"202603059159\",\"tag\":null,\"tags\":null,\"type\":\"article\"},{\"authors\":[{\"id\":\"738ca46e-ba6c-40a8-ae77-bbc3decb216a\",\"image\":{\"_type\":\"figure\",\"asset\":{\"_ref\":\"image-458176dea8c1412f42f2f27f894e5e1a89efc664-400x400-jpg\",\"_type\":\"reference\"},\"caption\":\"Behrouz Turani\"},\"name\":\"Behrouz Turani\",\"slug\":\"behrouz-turani\"}],\"headline\":\"Why Khamenei’s funeral keeps changing\",\"id\":\"a3f55ee6-b1f8-49b1-954c-81e055411842\",\"image\":{\"alt\":\"A car passes by a billboard of Iran's late Supreme Leader Ali Khamenei after he was killed in Israeli and US strikes, March 4, 2026.\",\"asset\":{\"_ref\":\"image-9a352eb18d31d847526ca1962e8730d995f92115-1200x800-jpg\",\"_type\":\"reference\"},\"crop\":{\"_type\":\"sanity.imageCrop\",\"bottom\":0.1627950621402953,\"left\":0.014805238134957044,\"right\":0.2654586148413824,\"top\":0.08424389023271332},\"hotspot\":{\"_type\":\"sanity.imageHotspot\",\"height\":0.7529610476269915,\"width\":0.7197361470236605,\"x\":0.3746733116467873,\"y\":0.460724414046209},\"metadata\":{\"dimensions\":{\"height\":800,\"width\":1200},\"lqip\":\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"}},\"language\":\"english\",\"lead\":[{\"_key\":\"bd428495596d\",\"_type\":\"block\",\"children\":[{\"_key\":\"5f32a8980334\",\"_type\":\"span\",\"marks\":[],\"text\":\"Funeral plans for Iran’s former Supreme Leader Ali Khamenei have been revised multiple times this week, reflecting mounting security fears, uncertainty over foreign attendance and unresolved questions about succession.\"}],\"markDefs\":[],\"style\":\"normal\"}],\"publishedAt\":\"2026-03-06T04:06:55.025Z\",\"shorthandUrl\":null,\"slug\":\"202603069419\",\"tag\":{\"color\":\"#0084bc\",\"id\":\"73b1863d-5f72-4a43-a578-40a59fc0e60b\",\"slug\":\"insight\",\"title\":\"INSIGHT\"},\"tags\":[{\"color\":\"#0084bc\",\"id\":\"73b1863d-5f72-4a43-a578-40a59fc0e60b\",\"slug\":\"insight\",\"title\":\"INSIGHT\"}],\"type\":\"article\"},{\"authors\":null,\"headline\":\"Iran says it hit Kurdish fighters near border, Iraqi Kurdish officials deny incursion\",\"id\":\"9a0ed2f3-62ad-4095-b8d7-4e1b8ac81397\",\"image\":{\"alt\":\"Iranian Kurdish fighters from the Kurdistan Freedom Party (PAK) take part in a training session at a base on the outskirts of Erbil, Iraq February 12, 2026.\",\"asset\":{\"_ref\":\"image-be04b7237c95ef4ecd1a64a3674faac149d3a4af-5500x3899-jpg\",\"_type\":\"reference\"},\"crop\":null,\"hotspot\":null,\"metadata\":{\"dimensions\":{\"height\":3899,\"width\":5500},\"lqip\":\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"}},\"language\":\"english\",\"lead\":[{\"_key\":\"41f71f21fbf8\",\"_type\":\"block\",\"children\":[{\"_key\":\"7862662f0cbb\",\"_type\":\"span\",\"marks\":[],\"text\":\"Iran’s intelligence ministry said it had struck positions of Kurdish fighters it accused of preparing to enter the country through its western borders, inflicting heavy losses on them, according to a statement carried by state media on Thursday.\"}],\"markDefs\":[],\"style\":\"normal\"}],\"publishedAt\":\"2026-03-05T12:05:22.124Z\",\"shorthandUrl\":null,\"slug\":\"202603058076\",\"tag\":null,\"tags\":null,\"type\":\"article\"}]},\"key\":\"c738eba003ed\",\"type\":\"mostview\"},{\"data\":{\"image\":{\"_type\":\"image\",\"asset\":{\"_ref\":\"image-e7802950c36d18d937b88453ade03b91460386ca-640x360-png\",\"_type\":\"reference\"}},\"url\":\"https://iranintl.com/newsletter\"},\"key\":\"3b5348ca699d\",\"type\":\"banner\"},{\"data\":{\"image\":{\"_type\":\"image\",\"asset\":{\"_ref\":\"image-caa18b2020a626df3d0b9232b436ebdda164b52d-640x360-png\",\"_type\":\"reference\"}},\"url\":\"https://www.iranintl.com/en/program/eye-for-iran\"},\"key\":\"001b9474d64f\",\"type\":\"banner\"}],\"language\":\"english\",\"className\":\"page__sidebar home__widgets\"}]\n"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"2c:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"home__clusters home__clusters--core\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L16\",\"core-c43b53efc5af\",{\"clusterKey\":\"c43b53efc5af\",\"clusterType\":\"daily\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"cluster cluster--coreCoverage\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"header\",null,{\"className\":\"ClusterHeader-module-scss-module__YSLH0a__header\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"ClusterHeader-module-scss-module__YSLH0a__header__title\",\"children\":\"In Case You Missed It\"}],null]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"DailyReportCluster-module-scss-module__mBywQG__container\",\"children\":[[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"DailyReportCluster-module-scss-module__mBywQG__featured\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",\"7512384e-8848-486e-8b7d-855a93ff3566\",{\"className\":\"DailyReportCluster-m